spec_data.Name: perl-Test-CheckManifest
spec_data.Description:
This package checks whether the Manifest file matches the distro or not. To
match a distro the Manifest has to name all files that come along with the
distribution.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 04:40:06 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Check if your Manifest matches your distro
